SUMMARY:Cloud Native AI + Kubeflow Day Hosted by CNCF - Full-Day Event | ALL ACCESS PASS REQUIRED
DESCRIPTION:Cloud Native AI + Kubeflow Day schedule is now LIVE!\n\nAI is advancing at an unprecedented pace\, from Large Language Models (LLMs) and Graph RAGs to new frameworks for ethical and responsible innovation. At the center of this evolution is Kubeflow\, the cloud-native ecosystem enabling data scientists\, ML engineers\, and AI practitioners to build\, deploy\, and scale AI/ML workloads.\nThis event brings together the Kubeflow community\, MLOps professionals\, and AI enthusiasts to explore real-world patterns\, cutting-edge tools\, and production-ready solutions. Whether you’re new to AI or an experienced practitioner\, you’ll gain valuable insights\, hands-on knowledge\, and connections that will shape the future of AI in the cloud-native world.&nbsp\;To learn more please visit the event's&nbsp\;website.For questions regarding this event\, please reach out to&nbsp\;cncfcolocatedevents@linuxfoundation.org.&nbsp\;
CATEGORIES:CNCF-HOSTED CO-LOCATED EVENTS
LOCATION:Hall 7 | Room B (Track 1) + Room C (Track 2)\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
