DTSTART:20260323T094800Z
DTEND:20260323T095300Z
SUMMARY:Project Lightning Talk: Blocking Vulnerable Workloads Out (And Catching What Got In) - Flavio Castelli\, Maintainer
DESCRIPTION:Keeping vulnerable workloads out of Kubernetes clusters is only half the battle. It's just as important to continuously monitor the workloads already running and quickly identify those that become vulnerable when new CVEs are disclosed. In this lightning talk\, you’ll learn how Kubewarden helps platform teams enforce image security at admission and maintain ongoing visibility into emerging risks.
CATEGORIES:PROJECT OPPORTUNITIES
LOCATION:Elicium 2\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
