SUMMARY:Project Lightning Talk: Harbor Update - Prasanth Baskar\, Maintainer
DESCRIPTION:In this lightning talk\, Harbor maintainers share a fast-paced update on the project’s latest progress. We’ll highlight what shipped in Harbor 2.14 and 2.15\, including key improvements in security\, operations\, and maintainability driven by real-world usage.\n\nWe’ll also preview what’s coming next on the Harbor roadmap\, from upcoming features to active design discussions\, and how the community can get involved. Join us for a quick snapshot of where Harbor is today and where it’s headed next.
CATEGORIES:PROJECT OPPORTUNITIES
