BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260303T114022Z
DTSTART:20260323T143800Z
DTEND:20260323T144300Z
SUMMARY:Project Lightning Talk: PipeCDv1 Is Here! Leverage The Power Of Plugin Architecture - Khanh Tran\, Maintainer
DESCRIPTION:PipeCD provides a unified and easy-to-understand interface that helps you easily achieve progressive delivery for a variety of application platforms at all levels\, from a single project to a large organization. After a year of development since our last KubeCon\, the pluggable architecture piped has been released in alpha and is ready to support community plugins.\n\nAdditionally\, numerous performance improvements and a brand-new feature called Deployment Trace have been implemented\, supporting the smooth creation of a CD platform that can handle tens of thousands of deployments with a single Control Plane.\n\nGet the latest update of PipeCD v1 alpha now and if you are struggling with managing deployment pipelines in complex multi-component systems\, give it a try!
CATEGORIES:PROJECT OPPORTUNITIES
LOCATION:Elicium 2\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
SEQUENCE:0
UID:2bbec61ab8baaf626ef8782329de2026
URL:http://kccnceu2026.sched.com/event/2bbec61ab8baaf626ef8782329de2026
END:VEVENT
